CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776125001
OL,3,C65,000 young people to be offered
OL,4,Cdefence, clean energy and digital
OL,5,Ctraining
OL,7,FAround 65,000 young people will be
OL,8,Fable to train to enter the defence,
OL,9,Fclean energy, digital and
OL,10,Fmanufacturing industries under the
OL,11,Flatest round of Government investment
OL,12,Finto colleges.
OL,14,FThe Government will provide #175
OL,15,Fmillion for 19 new Technical
OL,16,FExcellence Colleges across the country
OL,17,Fto deliver training in sectors deemed
OL,18,Fimportant for the future of the UK.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776125001
OL,3,C65,000 young people to be offered
OL,4,Cdefence, clean energy and digital
OL,5,Ctraining
OL,7,FMinister for skills Baroness Jacqui
OL,8,FSmith said the investment would help
OL,9,Fbuild a pipeline of skilled workers
OL,10,Ffor industries key to Britain's future.
OL,12,FThe Government has identified the
OL,13,Fareas most likely to help grow the
OL,14,Feconomy, Baroness Smith told the Press
OL,15,FAssociation, and said given the war
OL,16,Fhappening in the Middle East, the UK
OL,17,Fneeded to be able to support different
OL,18,Fways of getting its energy.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776125001
OL,3,C65,000 young people to be offered
OL,4,Cdefence, clean energy and digital
OL,5,Ctraining
OL,7,F"The Clean Energy (technical
OL,8,Fexcellence colleges) that we're
OL,9,Fannouncing today will help us to
OL,10,Fdevelop that to speed up our shift to
OL,11,Fclean energy, to protect our energy
OL,12,Fsupply and to help people with their
OL,13,Fbills," she said.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776125001
OL,3,C65,000 young people to be offered
OL,4,Cdefence, clean energy and digital
OL,5,Ctraining
OL,7,F"In the area of defence, where, given
OL,8,Fthe instability and some of the new
OL,9,Fchallenges to our defence in the
OL,10,Fworld, and our contribution to that,
OL,11,Fthis Government has pledged a big
OL,12,Fincrease in defence spending that
OL,13,Fneeds to support our armed forces and
OL,14,Four capacity, but that spending also
OL,15,Fneeds to deliver quality jobs to the
OL,16,FUK defence industry, who will need
OL,17,Fskilled people in order to be able to
OL,18,Fdeliver it."
OL,26,@oD@AOUzD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
