OL,3,C65,000 young people to be offered
OL,4,Cdefence, clean energy and digital
OL,5,Ctraining
OL,7,FIt is estimated nearly 600,000
OL,8,Fadditional workers will be needed in
OL,9,Fthese key sectors by 2030, the
OL,10,FDepartment for Education said.
OL,12,FIf follows the first wave of 10
OL,13,Ftechnical excellence colleges
OL,14,Fannounced last year specialising in
OL,15,Fconstruction.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
