OL,3,C65,000 young people to be offered
OL,4,Cdefence, clean energy and digital
OL,5,Ctraining
OL,7,FPrime Minister Sir Keir Starmer said:
OL,8,F"I want every young person to know
OL,9,Fthere is a clear route into wellpaid
OL,10,Fwork, whatever their background. These
OL,11,Fcolleges put technical skills front
OL,12,Fand centre, opening up highquality
OL,13,Fjobs in the industries driving
OL,14,FBritain's future.
OL,16,F"We are backing talent across the
OL,17,Fcountry, strengthening our workforce
OL,18,Fand making sure opportunity is built
OL,19,Finto the system ` not left to chance."
OL,26,@pD@AOUxD@AOU{D@fO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
