OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776125001
OL,3,C65,000 young people to be offered
OL,4,Cdefence, clean energy and digital
OL,5,Ctraining
OL,7,FThe colleges may spend the funding
OL,8,Fthey receive on specialist equipment,
OL,9,Fdeveloping new courses, training more
OL,10,Fspecialist staff, and more.
OL,12,FOn Monday, Baroness Smith met students
OL,13,Fand staff at Milton Keynes College,
OL,14,Fselected as a technical excellence
OL,15,Fcollege for digital, where students
OL,16,Fare already learning about robotics
OL,17,Fand artificial intelligence (AI).
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
