FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776125001
OL,3,C65,000 young people to be offered
OL,4,Cdefence, clean energy and digital
OL,5,Ctraining
OL,7,FIt comes after the latest figures
OL,8,Fshowed nearly a million (957,000) 16
OL,9,Fto 24-year-olds were "Neet" (not in
OL,10,Feducation, employment or training) in
OL,11,FOctober to December 2025.
OL,13,FThe high number of young people who
OL,14,Fwere Neet was a "loss of opportunity"
OL,15,Fand a "loss for the country", Baroness
OL,16,FSmith told PA.
OL,18,F"That's why we need really high-
OL,19,Fquality provision for young people
OL,20,Fbetween 16 to 19 to be able to
OL,21,Faccess," she said.
OL,26,@qD@VOUqD@[O]vD@QOUvD@eO]wD@GOUwD@\O]zD@
OL,26,AAOU}D@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776125001
OL,3,C65,000 young people to be offered
OL,4,Cdefence, clean energy and digital
OL,5,Ctraining
OL,7,F"We need our schools to better
OL,8,Fidentify the young people who are
OL,9,Fpotentially going to become Neet, we
OL,10,Fneed them to take responsibility for
OL,11,Fmaking sure that young people have got
OL,12,Fthe places, the college places, the
OL,13,Fapprenticeships, the jobs to go into.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776125001
OL,3,C65,000 young people to be offered
OL,4,Cdefence, clean energy and digital
OL,5,Ctraining
OL,7,F"And we need brilliant colleges like
OL,8,FMilton Keynes, where I am today, to be
OL,9,Fsupported, to be able to provide the
OL,10,Fopportunities for young people who
OL,11,Fwould otherwise be lost at such a
OL,12,Fcrucial time in their lives and for
OL,13,Fthe future of the skills that we need
OL,14,Fas a country as well."
OL,16,FThe Government has set a target for
OL,17,Ftwo-thirds of young people to be in
OL,18,Fhigher education, higher-level
OL,19,Ftraining or doing a gold standard
OL,20,Fapprenticeship by age 25.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
