OL,3,C65,000 young people to be offered
OL,4,Cdefence, clean energy and digital
OL,5,Ctraining
OL,7,FJawad Al Midani, 21, started studying
OL,8,Fat Milton Keynes College for a Level 1
OL,9,Fcourse, and has since worked his way
OL,10,Fup to studying for a Higher National
OL,11,FDiploma (HND) in cyber security.
OL,13,F"I feel as soon as I finish my
OL,14,Fqualifications I'll be ready to start
OL,15,Fmy career," he told PA.
OL,26,@uD@AOUwD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/13
