PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776125001
OL,3,C65,000 young people to be offered
OL,4,Cdefence, clean energy and digital
OL,5,Ctraining
OL,7,FChristian Proctor, 18, who is studying
OL,8,Ffor a Higher National Certificate
OL,9,F(HNC) in games design and will go on
OL,10,Fto an HND next year, said he was
OL,11,Fconfident the skills he was learning
OL,12,Fwould equip him for the next step once
OL,13,Fhe finished college.
OL,15,FThe 19 new Technical Excellence
OL,16,FColleges are as follows:
OL,18,FClean Energy
OL,20,FDigital and Technologies
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/13
